Welcome to Shallot:

This is a pretty much alpha release.

You'll need:

	PyAudioPlay
	Cymbeline
	(both available from StackWorks)
	eyeD3
	Either MySQL or SQLite and the appropiate Python bindings


Setup directions:
	Change the root of your music library:	
		In shallot/LibScanner.py

	